snippet.title: Tauronos trailer 2017
snippet.description:
Vote for us on Steam Greenlight : http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=897686514
TAURONOS is an indie game about exploring a dark labyrinth, praying to the gods for favors and avoiding traps, all while the ferocious Minotaur chases after you.
